                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6474" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0130</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11384 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内外兼修：京博集团的社会责任实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">External and Internal Cultivation: Social Responsibility Practice of Chambroad Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许长勇，刘妍，高虹，代雨</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">河北工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东京博控股集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">化学工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">战略型企业社会责任；共享价值；京博集团；2022百优案例；微案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Strategic corporate social responsibility; Shared value; Chambroad Group</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东京博控股集团有限公司是一家地处山东省滨州市博兴县以石油化工为主导产业的民营企业。在集团董事局主席马韵升的带领下，京博秉持以“仁孝”为核心的企业文化，从企业发展战略高度谋划企业社会责任行为，很好地契合了波特的“战略型企业社会责任”理念。案例描述了京博集团发展过程中两类典型的社会责任实践：一是创造性地处理“三废”，大力发展废物产业，由内及外地解决价值链主导型社会问题，兼顾了企业社会责任与竞争优势提升；二是构建N1N校企联融平台，打造产教融合新模式，由外及内地解决竞争环境主导型社会问题，实现了企业社会责任与经营环境改善的融合。通过本案例的研讨，能够帮助学生深刻理解和掌握“战略型企业社会责任”的概念和内涵。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Shandong Chambroad Holding Group Co., Ltd. is a private enterprise located in Boxing County, Binzhou City, Shandong Province, with petrochemical industry as its leading industry. Under the leadership of Ma Yunsheng, Chambroad adheres to the corporate culture with &quot;benevolence and filial piety&quot; as the core, and plans corporate social responsibility behaviors from the height of enterprise development strategy, which fits Porter&#39;s concept of &quot;strategic corporate social responsibility&quot; well. The case describes two typical social responsibility practices in the development of Chambroad Group: First, creatively deal with the &quot;three wastes&quot;, vigorously develop the waste industry, solve the social problems dominated by the value chain from the inside out, and take into account social responsibility and competitive advantage enhancement; The second is to build N1N school-enterprise integration platform, create a new mode of integration of production and education, solve social problems dominated by competitive environment from the outside in, and realize the integration of corporate social responsibility and business environment improvement. Through the discussion of this case, it can help students deeply understand and master the concept and connotation of &quot;strategic corporate social responsibility&quot;.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商业伦理与企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">价值链主导型社会问题；价值链模型；企业社会责任；由内及外：解决价值链主导型社会问题；竞争环境主导型社会问题；钻石模型；企业社会责任；由外及内：解决竞争环境主导型社会问题；社会问题的分类；共享价值；战略型企业社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
